	<p><em><strong>Paul</strong> replies:</em> Maybe back in the good old days, politicians might have listened to the 2 million people matching in London against the Iraq war, and they might not have been the lying, two faced, media whores that we have to settle for these days.</p>
	<small>
	written 15th Apr 2005 <!-- | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=867&amp;commentid=856">abusive?</a>
